kaizen - Continously improve, build and manage free software
============================================================

About
-----

kaizen is a tool to build, install and maintain your software and is written in
[Python] [1]

Requirements
------------

 * python 2.6 or higher
 * kommons - https://github.com/bjoernricks/kommons
 * argparse - https://pypi.python.org/pypi/argparse (when using python 2.6)


[1]: http://www.python.org
